name: Swinca
public_notice: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
Swinca's mission is to allow anyone to become a landlord by oering the possibility
to invest instantly in real estate worldwide by the real estate tokenization.
The investors receive their share of the rents, as well as the respective capital gains of their investments.
